  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00313', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-101-bceca813', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-02', NULL, 'essay', '建築改良物如為課稅目的而估價，應採用何種方法較為適宜？請說明該方法之估價
