  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00314', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-101-bceca813', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-02', NULL, 'essay', '價值、價格、成本之意義有何區別？其與成本法、比較法及收益法有何關聯？試申
